		{"bg", id=18, file="rcg01010103", x=0, y=0, path=":cg/rcg01/", lv=18, ev=1, bx=800, by=450},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="rei1040", path=":vo/", ch="rei"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“You’re amazing, seriously. You managed to change Seiran Island twice. You saved Fumino, you saved Akino... And not just them, either. Me, and so many others...”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“……你真是了不起呢。再次改变了青蓝岛。拯救了文乃，也拯救了秋野……不但只是如此。我和许多人也……”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "禮"},
					"「……你真是了不起呢。再次改變了青藍島。拯救了文乃，也拯救了秋野……不但只是如此。我和許多人也……」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00072",
		linknext = "0058_00074",
		line = 1247,
	},
	["0058_00074"] = {
		{"fg", file="jun_01f_00001", file1="jun_01f_00101", file3="jun_01f_00309", file4="jun_01f_00401", path=":fg/jun_01f/", id=30, ch="淳之介", mw="mw", mode=1, sync=0, x=-5, y=-5, lv=3},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“I think you’re overestimating my role in this. It’s all thanks to the people who helped me along the way. Not to mention the fact that some of them hate my guts.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“……你过奖了。不管是哪件事都是因为我有伙伴才能做到，也肯定会有在背后憎恨着我的人吧。”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"「……妳過獎了。不管是哪件事都是因為我有夥伴才能做到，也肯定會有在背後憎恨著我的人吧。」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00073",
		linknext = "0058_00075",
		line = 1259,
	},
	["0058_00075"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“Besides, if we’re talking about saving Mizuhiki, surely the credit has to go to Touka?”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“而且，如果是说救了水引酱这件事──实际上真正做到的桐香，不是吗？”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"「而且，如果是說救了水引醬這件事──實際上真正做到的桐香，不是嗎？」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00074",
		linknext = "0058_00076",
		line = 1270,
	},
	["0058_00076"] = {
		{"cgdel", id=18, lv=18, time=0, alphadel=1, evmaskoff=1},
		{"bg", id=18, file="rcg01010102", x=0, y=0, path=":cg/rcg01/", lv=18, ev=1, bx=800, by=450},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="rei1041", path=":vo/", ch="rei"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“Even so, Miss Touka just gave Akino a place to be. You were the one who changed her heart.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“即使是这样。桐香大人也只是给了秋野容身之处。而你却是解开了她的心结……”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "禮"},
					"「即使是這樣。桐香大人也只是給了秋野容身之處。而你卻是解開了她的心結……」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00075",
		linknext = "0058_00077",
		line = 1286,
	},
	["0058_00077"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="rei1042", path=":vo/", ch="rei"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“If you give all the credit to your friends, it makes it sound like you’re just a nice guy who’s got a lot of friends.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“若说这全都要归功于伙伴的话，那也是因为你拥有能让这些伙伴追随着你的东西吧。”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "禮"},
					"「若說這全都要歸功於夥伴的話，那也是因為你擁有能讓這些夥伴追隨著你的東西吧。」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00076",
		linknext = "0058_00078",
		line = 1298,
	},
	["0058_00078"] = {
		{"cgdel", id=18, lv=18, time=0, alphadel=1, evmaskoff=1},
		{"bg", id=18, file="rcg01010101", x=0, y=0, path=":cg/rcg01/", lv=18, ev=1, bx=800, by=450},
		{"transitiontime", time=300},
		{"text"},
		text = {
			vo = {
				{"vo", file="rei1043", path=":vo/", ch="rei"},
			},
			ja = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "Rei"},
					"“The whole reason I’m able to laugh about it now is you, and what you did.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"礼"},
					"“……让我能这么笑着，也几乎都是多亏有了你呢。”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					name = {"礼", "禮"},
					"「……讓我能這麼笑著，也幾乎都是多虧有了你呢。」",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00077",
		linknext = "0058_00079",
		line = 1314,
	},
	["0058_00079"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"I’ve received a lot of compliments, but this one feels special. It’s kind of embarrassing.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"虽然至今为止被夸赞过很多次，但是像这样的说法还是第一次呢──格外的难为情呢。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"雖然至今為止被誇讚過很多次，但是像這樣的說法還是第一次呢──格外的難為情呢。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00078",
		linknext = "0058_00080",
		line = 1324,
	},
	["0058_00080"] = {
		{"text"},
		text = {
			ja = {
				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"It makes me want to deflect it somehow with a joke instead of continuing to be awkward.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"想开开玩笑来盖过这种心痒难耐的感觉。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			tw = {
				{
					"想開開玩笑來蓋過這種心癢難耐的感覺。",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
		},
		linkback = "0058_00079",
		linknext = "0058_00081",
		line = 1334,
	},
	["0058_00081"] = {
		{"fg", file="jun_01f_00001", file1="jun_01f_00101", file2="jun_01f_00207", file4="jun_01f_00401", path=":fg/jun_01f/", id=30, ch="淳之介", mw="mw", mode=1, sync=0, x=-5, y=-5, lv=3},
		{"text"},
